name: NFTYPUP TALES VOLUME 2
description: VOLUME 2: THE JOURNEY BEGINS. Hiro left his home in Wolf Castle and began his journey down the mountain. He planned to visit the Starwatcher in Dingo Dunes to seek her advice. As he passed the Howling Caves he was stopped by a voice. 'Take me with you!' A young pup emerged from the darkness. . .a reclusive member of the rival pack, The Howlers! Falling stars were causing quakes in the underground caves. Hemlock was the only pup brave enough to surface and seek a solution! Hiro decided to put aside their differences and bring Lock along on his quest! To be continued! .......Created by @NFTYpups. Music by Shakira Knightley.
